        "notes": "This API requires participation by websites and email providers. We successfully ran a devtrial with a few partners which we expect will join us running an original trial.\n\nBased on what we heard so far, we are optimistic this will hit a sweet spot with website authors, but that we'd like to gather further evidence of developer demand and API fitness in an actual production setup."
